From: Kairo Authors <kairo@research>
Date: Wed Jun 24 17:00:00 2026 +0000
Subject: [RFC/POC] 0026: blk-cgroup AI I/O controller scaffold

RFC/POC — Not for LKML submission.

Add a conceptual blk-cgroup AI I/O controller scaffold that maps Kairo
request classes to cgroup-level policy.

Real AI inference runs in containers, services, tenants, and jobs.
Today the block cgroup subsystem (blk-cgroup, blk-iocost, blk-throttle)
does not understand AI inference I/O patterns. Kairo's per-request
classification (decode, prefetch, prefill, eviction) should eventually
be connected to cgroup-level budgets and policies.

This patch adds:

  enum kairo_blkg_policy_class
    KAIRO_BLKG_DEFAULT
    KAIRO_BLKG_PRODUCTION_DECODE
    KAIRO_BLKG_BATCH_PREFILL
    KAIRO_BLKG_PREFETCH
    KAIRO_BLKG_EVICTION
    KAIRO_BLKG_BACKGROUND

  struct kairo_blkg_policy
    policy_class, target_decode_p99_us, decode_weight,
    prefetch_weight, write_weight, eviction_weight,
    allow_recompute_eviction, enable_adaptive_controller,
    enable_model_fairness

  struct kairo_blkg_stats
    decode_dispatches, prefetch_dispatches, prefill_writes,
    evictions, throttled_prefetches, demoted_writes,
    latency_violations

Conceptual hooks:

  kairo_blkg_policy_from_request(struct request *rq)
  kairo_blkg_allow_decode(struct request *rq)
  kairo_blkg_throttle_prefetch(struct request *rq)
  kairo_blkg_demote_write(struct request *rq)
  kairo_blkg_account_dispatch(struct request *rq)

These are CONCEPTUAL-HOOK points with LINUX-6.8-CHECK annotations.
They are not wired into the dispatch path.

Conceptual cgroup interface files (scaffold only, no filesystem
implementation):

  kairo.policy_class
  kairo.target_decode_p99_us
  kairo.decode_weight
  kairo.prefetch_weight
  kairo.write_weight
  kairo.eviction_weight
  kairo.allow_recompute_eviction

Sysfs counters (for eventual registration):

  kairo_blkg_decode_dispatches
  kairo_blkg_prefetch_dispatches
  kairo_blkg_prefill_writes
  kairo_blkg_evictions
  kairo_blkg_throttled_prefetches
  kairo_blkg_demoted_writes
  kairo_blkg_latency_violations

LINUX-6.8-CHECK:
  block/blk-cgroup.c:         struct blkcg, struct blkcg_gq, blkg_lookup
  block/blk-iocost.c:         ioc_weight_parse pattern for cgroup knobs
  block/blk-throttle.c:       throtl_pd_alloc/free for policy data
  include/linux/blk-cgroup.h: blkcg_policy, blkcg_policy_register

Signed-off-by: Kairo Authors <kairo@research>
